Privacy Policy for Type  Racer

This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which Type Racer ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, maintains, and discloses information collected from users ("you" or "users") of the Type Racer ("app"). This Privacy Policy applies to the app and all products and services offered by Hollie.

Information Collection and Usage

Type Racer does not collect any user data, personal information, We do not have access to, store, or share any content that is processed through the app. The app operates solely on your device and does not transmit any data to our servers or any third parties.

Cookies and Tracking Technologies

Type Racer does not use cookies, tracking technologies, or any other methods to gather information about your usage of the app or your device.

Third-Party Services

Type Racer does not integrate or utilize any third-party services, libraries, or frameworks that would result in data collection, tracking, or sharing.

Security

We take the security of your data seriously. Since we do not collect or store any user data, your information is inherently secure from our end. The conversion process takes place locally on your device.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

Type Racer may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by updating the "Last Updated" date at the beginning of the policy. We encourage users to review this page periodically for any changes. Your continued use of the app after any modifications to the Privacy Policy will constitute your acknowledgment of the changes and your consent to abide and be bound by the modified Privacy Policy.

Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or the app, please contact us at hello@haydendoesdev.com

This Privacy Policy was last updated on April 31, 2025.
